    <exercise xml:id="exercise-compare-within-jumping">
      <statement>
      <p>
        [<em>Dataset</em>: <c>Jumping</c>] <xref ref="hebert2023effect"/> recorded double-legged jumping distance for <m>80</m> healthy people, when they wore shoes and were barefoot (data below).
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li><p>What do the differences mean (as given in the table)?</p></li>
        <li><p>Create a plot of the data.</p></li>
        <li><p>Create a numerical summary table for the data.</p></li>
